reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater nice-looking, feminine, and incredibly soft, with great workmanship and color accuracy. They describe it as comfortable and warm, with one customer noting it's perfect for spring. The size receives mixed feedback - while some say the large size fits well, others find it runs large with sleeves that are too long. items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Flattering and cool, size down
items.body: The material is soft. Size down one size. I usually wear XL, but the Large fit well. Great sweater if your body runs hot. The material has holes the way it’s knitted so you still get the sweater look without sweating. You’ll want to wear a spaghetti strap tank top or tshirt under it. Read more
items.author: Cola55

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Terrific chic hangout sweater
items.body: Stunning on - really soft and comfortable but it looks really good on. It has shape but it’s also just the right bit of slouchy. Wore it with faded denim and it looked great Read more
items.author: S. Vora

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Soft, comfortable and colors as expected
items.body: The sweater is incredibly soft and very comfortable. I bought two in different colors. It does run large. I usually wear a medium, but I bought the small. If they had an extra small, I probably would’ve gotten that one. I am 142 pounds and 5’4”. But the Small is perfectly fine. I am keeping tgem. The style of the sleeves are a little bigger and then they come down and taper to the wrist. I like that but some may not. It is not a winter sweater for sure. Definitely need a camisole or something underneath it. Still looks great with jeans. I haven’t washed it yet. It does seem a little fragile so I probably would not put it in the dryer. Read more
items.author: kathleen

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Loose Knit Allows Peak of Under Garment
items.body: A little disappointed in this sweater. It is a nice cinnamon color, however, the sleeves were too long and the holes in the knit design allowed peaking of my under garment. Overall knit is a very loose knit. I regretfully had to return the sweater. Read more
items.author: Cheryl Fua

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Sweater Find
items.body: The perfect fall sweater light and airy, but super comfortable, & warm. The fit is good The color is very black not like faded. Really good quality overall. Read more
items.author: Lisa

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just like the pic
items.body: Beautiful sweater just like the pic Read more
items.author: ScottiHS

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Damaged
items.body: Cute sweater but unfortunately it came with 3 holes in it. I will try to reorder & see if the next one come as it should. Read more
items.author: Hammerhead

items.title: 2.0 out of 5 stars Sleeves way too long
items.body: The pros of this sweater are the color options, style, softness, light weight. The cons are the sleeves are excessively long, random loose threads everywhere, price and quality dont align. I wanted to love it so much that I tried tucking the shoulder under my bra strap a little to 'shorten' the sleeves. And the sleeves are billowing at the wrist so you cannot fold them up. Unfortunate that the fit is odd like that, because visually its a nice looking sweater in the picture. Read more
items.author: TaylorsMom

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve V Neck is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve V Neck is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: A White, Yl-khaki, D Chestnut, D Caramel, Yl-dblue, C Dblue, C Reddish Brown, B Black, C Red, Pa Wine Red, D Army Green, D Wine Red, Yl-black, B Lake Blue. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
